name: NoisyJungle
0:
”Alexa, ask Noisy Jungle what sound does a monkey make?”
”Alexa, ask Noisy Jungle what sound does a tiger make?”
”Alexa, ask Noisy Jungle what sound does a snake make?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: noisy jungle
des: Makes the sound of a jungle animal on request. Examples are monkey, gorilla, tiger, jaguar, bat, snake, elephant or parrot.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
